Requirements:
    Follow design spec - https://www.figma.com/design/UqGFBvDEFaqtKvq7ZgJAN2/Mobile-Restaurant-Menu-(Copy)?node-id=0-1&p=f&t=pQg4diw05byEvDqz-0
    Render the menu options using JavaScript
    Be able to add/remove items
    Have a payment modal with compulsory form inputs
    Print thank you message when payment complete

Stretch Goals
    Change the theme
    Offer a "meal deal" discount
    Allow users to rate their experience
    Remove ability to use buttons when "complete order has been selected"
    Add ability to go back to edit order